-- BP, RWE Agree to Adjust Two Energy Accords With Egypt, Oil Ministry Says
-- Ola Galal
-- 2010-07-19T08:02:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-19/bp-rwe-agree-to-adjust-two-energy-accords-with-egypt-oil-ministry-says.html

          
          
             BP Plc and RWE AG agreed to adjust
two oil agreements with Egypt, the country’s Oil Ministry said
in a statement distributed in Cairo today. The adjustments
include “huge advantages” for Egypt, it said.  
